14#ifndef RDATA_GENERIC_NS_2_C
15#define RDATA_GENERIC_NS_2_C
16
17#define RRTYPE_NS_ATTRIBUTES (DNS_RDATATYPEATTR_ZONECUTAUTH)
18
19static inline isc_result_t
20fromtext_ns(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
21 isc_token_t token;
22 dns_name_t name;
23 isc_buffer_t buffer;
24 bool ok;
25
26 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_ns);
27
28 UNUSED(type);
29 UNUSED(rdclass);
30 UNUSED(callbacks);
31
32 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token,isc_tokentype_string,
33 false));
34
35 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
36 buffer_fromregion(&buffer, &token.value.as_region);
37 if (origin == NULL)
38 origin = dns_rootname;
39 RETTOK(dns_name_fromtext(&name, &buffer, origin, options, target));
40 ok = true;
41 if ((options & DNS_RDATA_CHECKNAMES) != 0)
42 ok = dns_name_ishostname(&name, false);
43 if (!ok && (options & DNS_RDATA_CHECKNAMESFAIL) != 0)
44 RETTOK(DNS_R_BADNAME);
45 if (!ok && callbacks != NULL)
46 warn_badname(&name, lexer, callbacks);
47 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
48}
49
50static inline isc_result_t
51totext_ns(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
52 isc_region_t region;
53 dns_name_t name;
54 dns_name_t prefix;
55 bool sub;
56
57 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_ns);
58 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
59
60 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
61 dns_name_init(&prefix, NULL);
62
63 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
64 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
65
66 sub = name_prefix(&name, tctx->origin, &prefix);
67
68 return (dns_name_totext(&prefix, sub, target));
69}
70
71static inline isc_result_t
72fromwire_ns(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
73 dns_name_t name;
74
75 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_ns);
76
77 UNUSED(type);
78 UNUSED(rdclass);
79
80 dns_decompress_setmethods(dctx, DNS_COMPRESS_GLOBAL14);
81
82 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
83 return (dns_name_fromwire(&name, source, dctx, options, target));
84}
85
86static inline isc_result_t
87towire_ns(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
88 dns_name_t name;
89 dns_offsets_t offsets;
90 isc_region_t region;
91
92 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_ns);
93 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
94
95 dns_compress_setmethods(cctx, DNS_COMPRESS_GLOBAL14);
96
97 dns_name_init(&name, offsets);
98 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
99 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
100
101 return (dns_name_towire(&name, cctx, target));
102}
103
104static inline int
105compare_ns(ARGS_COMPARE) {
106 dns_name_t name1;
107 dns_name_t name2;
108 isc_region_t region1;
109 isc_region_t region2;
110
111 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
112 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
113 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_ns);
114 REQUIRE(rdata1->length != 0);
115 REQUIRE(rdata2->length != 0);
116
117 dns_name_init(&name1, NULL);
118 dns_name_init(&name2, NULL);
119
120 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &region1);
121 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &region2);
122
123 dns_name_fromregion(&name1, &region1);
124 dns_name_fromregion(&name2, &region2);
125
126 return (dns_name_rdatacompare(&name1, &name2));
127}
128
129static inline isc_result_t
130fromstruct_ns(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
131 dns_rdata_ns_t *ns = source;
132 isc_region_t region;
133
134 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_ns);
135 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
136 REQUIRE(ns->common.rdtype == type);
137 REQUIRE(ns->common.rdclass == rdclass);
138
139 UNUSED(type);
140 UNUSED(rdclass);
141
142 dns_name_toregion(&ns->name, &region);
143 return (isc_buffer_copyregion(target, &region));
144}
145
146static inline isc_result_t
147tostruct_ns(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
148 isc_region_t region;
149 dns_rdata_ns_t *ns = target;
150 dns_name_t name;
151
152 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_ns);
153 REQUIRE(target != NULL);
154 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
155
156 ns->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
157 ns->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
158 ISC_LINK_INIT(&ns->common, link);
159
160 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
161 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
162 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
163 dns_name_init(&ns->name, NULL);
164 RETERR(name_duporclone(&name, mctx, &ns->name));
165 ns->mctx = mctx;
166 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
167}
168
169static inline void
170freestruct_ns(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
171 dns_rdata_ns_t *ns = source;
172
173 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
174
175 if (ns->mctx == NULL)
176 return;
177
178 dns_name_free(&ns->name, ns->mctx);
179 ns->mctx = NULL;
180}
181
182static inline isc_result_t
183additionaldata_ns(ARGS_ADDLDATA) {
184 dns_name_t name;
185 dns_offsets_t offsets;
186 isc_region_t region;
187
188 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_ns);
189
190 dns_name_init(&name, offsets);
191 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
192 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
193
194 return ((add)(arg, &name, dns_rdatatype_a));
195}
196
197static inline isc_result_t
198digest_ns(ARGS_DIGEST) {
199 isc_region_t r;
200 dns_name_t name;
201
202 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_ns);
203
204 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
205 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
206 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &r);
207
208 return (dns_name_digest(&name, digest, arg));
209}
210
211static inline bool
212checkowner_ns(ARGS_CHECKOWNER) {
213
214 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_ns);
215
216 UNUSED(name);
217 UNUSED(type);
218 UNUSED(rdclass);
219 UNUSED(wildcard);
220
221 return (true);
222}
223
224static inline bool
225checknames_ns(ARGS_CHECKNAMES) {
226 isc_region_t region;
227 dns_name_t name;
228
229 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_ns);
230
231 UNUSED(owner);
232
233 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
234 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
235 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
236 if (!dns_name_ishostname(&name, false)) {
237 if (bad != NULL)
238 dns_name_clone(&name, bad);
239 return (false);
240 }
241 return (true);
242}
243
244static inline int
245casecompare_ns(ARGS_COMPARE) {
246 return (compare_ns(rdata1, rdata2));
247}
